data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
This samples demonstrates the steps to provide runtime localizations for the charts.
1) Click on either of the charts to observe the chart's ShowProperties dialog. 2) Select the Chart(s) to localize and a prefix to insert before the existing strings. 3) Press the Add Selected Prefix button. 4) Click the newly localized chart and see the modified dialogs. 5) Press the Show PropertyGrid button, and note that Chart property descriptions in the property grid have also been localized. (Note, only chart properties and are localizable, not inherited control properties.)
